# USDM v4

This site is the generated reference documentation for the USDM v4 schema derived from the CDISC DDF-RA [dataStructure.yml](https://github.com/cdisc-org/DDF-RA/blob/aa303cb32f5d3ceecc68a16803e26720d2c1fc26/Deliverables/UML/dataStructure.yml) source model. It is intended to make the model easier to explore by publishing the schema as browsable documentation, including classes, slots, types, the relationships between them, and class instance examples.

Use this site to understand the overall shape of the model, inspect the meaning of each class and slot, review example instances for key classes, and navigate from high-level study concepts down to the detailed attributes captured in the LinkML representation.

